  "instructions": [
    "Preheat a non-stick frying pan over medium heat. Add sesame oil and let it warm up.",
    "Crack the egg into the pan, gently stirring while the yolk cooks to your desired consistency.",
    "Add minced garlic and chopped onion to the pan. Stir-fry for about 1-2 minutes until onions are translucent.",
    "Gradually pour in tomato sauce, stir well to combine all ingredients.",
    "Season with salt and black pepper according to taste. Let it simmer for another minute or so.",
    "Remove from heat and serve hot."
